      "post_number": 19,
      "username": "korriku",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/korriku/{size}/18544_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-03-01T01:24:26.010Z",
      "cooked": "<p>ja nje kerkim cfaredo me pyetjen ‘<a href=\"http://health.costhelper.com/knee-replacement.html\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">how much a knee replacement surgery cost</a>’</p>\n<p>$35,000.00 ne total, shpjegon.<br>\nPastaj e specifikon sa i bie se paguajme ne si paciente: Deductible, out-of-pocket, coinsurance.<br>\nPo te me pyesesh mua te dhenat e planit te siguracionit qe kam jane te ngjajshme me aty.<br>\nDmth pagesa nga xhepi im per ate operacion (larg qofte!) do ishte ~ $3000- $4500.<br>\nT’ia tregoje axhes keto shoku jot, qe te shkoje jo vete por duke kercyer te kirurgu.<br>\nHidhi nje sy faqes deri ne fund se ka te dhena nga burime te tjera.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 16,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 22657,
      "post_number": 20,
      "username": "Pjetermustakuqi",
      "name": "A.P",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/pjetermustakuqi/{size}/11417_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-03-01T05:48:00.589Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ai shoku e dinte kte pjese, sepse kishte shembuj me njerez konkret qe i kishin operu ne Turqi. Behej fjale qe kishin pagu 10 mije euro,nga 5 per secilin gju. Xhajes,meqe ne rini ka pas lujt futboll,i tha,- n’dash  me fillu me lujt prap futboll,hec t’shkojme t’vesh protezat.<br>\nMjeku i kishte thene, qe ne gjithe keto operacionet e venies se protezave qe aplikohen neper kocka,ai i gjurit eshte me i thjeshti.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 19,
      "like_count": 0
    },
